    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="la">
                    <ab>
                        <lb n="1"/>Claudio Petronio Probo <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iro</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimo</ex></expan></supplied>
                        <lb n="2"/>proconsuli Africae et <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acra</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ice</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>udicanti</ex></expan></supplied>,
                        <lb n="3"/>uno eodemque tempore <hi rend="supraline">I<unclear>I</unclear></hi> <supplied reason="lost">et <hi rend="supraline">III</hi></supplied>
                        <lb n="4"/>praetorio <sic>prefectura</sic> <expan><abbr>pol<supplied reason="lost">lent</supplied></abbr><supplied reason="lost"><ex>i</ex></supplied></expan>,
                        <lb n="5"/>consuli ordinario, nobilita<supplied reason="lost">te</supplied>
                        <lb n="6"/>munificentiaque <sic>praestante</sic>,
                        <lb n="7"/>originali patrono, regiones
                        <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character" precision="low"/> collegia posuerunt.
                    </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <p>Edition based on Chioffi 2005, with some original suggestions by Porena.</p>
                <p>
                    <app loc="2"><note>et s<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>: Chioffi 2005</note></app>
                    <app loc="2-5"><note>proconsuli Africae et s[imul] / uno eodemque tempor(e) et[iam] / praetorio prefectura pol[lenti], / consuli ordinario: Barbieri 1971; proconsuli Africae et s(acra) [v(ice) iud(icanti)], / uno eodemque tempore (e)t [inde ?] / praetorio prefectura pol[lenti], / consuli ordinario: Mazzarino 1974, p. 335, Giardina 1983, p. 171; proconsuli Africae et s(acra) [v(ice) iud(icanti)], / uno eodemque tempore et [in] / praetorio pr(a)efectura polle[nti et] / consuli ordinario: Chastagnol 1982; proconsuli Africae et s(acra) [v(ice) iud(icanti)], / uno eodemque tempore et[iam] / praetorio prefectura pol[lenti], / consuli ordinario: Cameron 1985</note></app>
                    <app loc="3"><note>tempor(e) et <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>: Chioffi 2005</note></app>
                    <app loc="4"><note>pr(a)efectura pol[lenti]: Chioffi 2005</note></app>
                    <app loc="6"><note>praestanti: Chioffi 2005</note></app>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>“To Claudius Petronius Probus, of clarissimus rank, proconsul of Africa and with jurisdiction on behalf of the emperor, at the same time in charge of his second and third praetorian prefecture, ordinary consul, superior for nobility and munificence, patron by origo, the regions and the colleges set up.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="fr">
                <p>“...”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p>“Al chiarissimo Claudius Petronius Probus, proconsole d’Africa con giurisdizione in vece dell’imperatore, che si fregia nel medesimo periodo della seconda e terza prefettura del pretorio, console ordinario, superiore per nobiltà e per munificenza, patrono legato dall’<foreign>origo</foreign>, le regioni ... i collegi posero.”</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>...</p>
            </div>
